  "detailed_description": "You are entrusted with the role of one of the elite captains, put on a high-tech mech suit suitable for travel into space and go on an exciting journey. Explore a galaxy full of adventures in the sci-fi game Deep Space and find new friends and acquaintances. Explore deep space, go to different planets and destroy dangerous enemies to save humanity from certain death.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- Eliminate the threat alone. Play a small campaign in single player mode.<br />\r\n- Explore a new hostile world.<br />\r\n- Embark on an exciting journey and save humanity.",
  "about_the_game": "You are entrusted with the role of one of the elite captains, put on a high-tech mech suit suitable for travel into space and go on an exciting journey. Explore a galaxy full of adventures in the sci-fi game Deep Space and find new friends and acquaintances. Explore deep space, go to different planets and destroy dangerous enemies to save humanity from certain death.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- Eliminate the threat alone. Play a small campaign in single player mode.<br />\r\n- Explore a new hostile world.<br />\r\n- Embark on an exciting journey and save humanity.",
